 Google, MSN, Yahoo!, Amazon, eBay, and most Web 2.0 plays.<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3"> Type 2 -- Generic Free Text Search, Open Search, GData and XQuery/XPath over HTTP</bridgehead>
