</itemizedlist><bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3"> Type 4 -- Generic Free Text Search, <ulink url="OpenSearch">OpenSearch</ulink>, GData, XQuery/XPath, and SPARQL</bridgehead>
